thread.title: Tania Menendez
thread.title_full: Yaniv & Associates, PC reviewed by Tania Menendez

author: Tania Menendez
title: Tania Menendez
text: At first I was hesitant to try an online divorce lawyer since there are so many scams all over the Internet. But as I was looking up reviews Yaniv and Associates seemed very legit. All the reviews were positive. It seemed too good to be true but it is very true. My divorce process was quick and easy. And they emailed me what was happening every step of the way. I paid the expedited cost and in less than 8 weeks my divorce is finalized. I am very satisfied and would recommend them to anyone.
